Package: gvcm
Type: Package
Title: Double Machine Learning for Generalized Varying Coefficient Models
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Maosen",
           family = "Peng",
           email = "mpeng1@mdanderson.org",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements a Double Machine Learning (DML) estimator for
    generalized varying coefficient models (GVCM) under canonical
    generalized linear model links. The package provides cross-fitted
    estimation of nuisance functions using regularized regression
    and inference for the average varying coefficient parameter.
